data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! PLUS $5,000 SELLER PAID CLOSING COST with an accepted offer that closes on or before January 31, 2024. Don't miss out on this Beautifully well kept three bedroom, two bathroom home in the coveted Miller Farm subdivision. Brand new roof put on October of 2023!! Large master bedroom with Double vanity in the master bathroom and large walk-in closet. Very spacious Living Room with open concept and also a split floor plan for added privacy. The home also has a fully fenced-in backyard with a fire pit, great for entertaining. Come and see this Great home before it's gone!!
